12728     // when any of these dependencies turn out an operand of another PHI, coming
12729     // from this same block, position of a stab instruction will become invalid.
12730     // The is because source vector that supposed to feed this gather node was
12731     // inserted at the end of the block [after stab instruction]. So we need
12732     // to adjust insertion point again to the end of block.
12733     if (isa<PHINode>(UserI)) {
